StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [sp_MISuccessfulImport]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
( @TargetImportID int, @SuccessfulImport char(1) OUTPUT )
AS
SELECT @SuccessfulImport = CASE WHEN (NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM MIRS_IMPORT_ERROR MIE WHERE MIE.MIRS_IMPORT_ID = @TargetImportID)) OR EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM ERROR_LOG EL INNER JOIN MIRS_IMPORT_ERROR MIE ON (MIE.MIRS_IMPORT_ID = @TargetImportID AND EL.ERROR_LOG_ID = MIE.ERROR_LOG_ID AND EL.STATUS = 'RESOLVED')) THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END
